Should we buy Oozora Construction? This minus...

659
01:03:49,096 --> 01:03:54,096
買えない！買えないよね。マイナス状態買えないですよ。
Can't buy! / You can't buy, right? You can't buy when it's in a minus state.

660
01:03:54,096 --> 01:03:56,596
マイナス状態買えない。マイナスはプラスになるまで...
You can't buy in a minus state. / Until the minus becomes plus...

661
01:03:56,596 --> 01:04:02,096
きゃー！ちょっと待ってよ。これさあ...
Kyaa! / Wait a minute. This...

662
01:04:02,096 --> 01:04:08,596
どうする？どうしたらいい？これ。どれもみんなプラスだよ。ししろフーズ...
What should I do? What's the best move here? / Everything is in the plus. Shishiro Foods...

663
01:04:08,596 --> 01:04:14,096
んな電がちょっとだけ上がったくらいで、もうなんか買わない方がいいのか。一回様子見るか。
Nna Railway only went up a little bit, so maybe I shouldn't buy anything else? / Let's wait and see for now.

664
01:04:14,096 --> 01:04:19,596
ねぽらぼ建設で頑張りたい。頑張らせていただきたい。
I want to work hard at NePoLaBo Construction. Please let me work hard there.

665
01:04:19,596 --> 01:04:23,596
え、どうなった？どうだった？株の変動注文は？全部プラス、ほぼ。
Wait, what happened? How was the stock change order? / Almost everything is in the plus.

666
01:04:23,596 --> 01:04:30,096
え、ねぽらぼが...跳ねた？跳ねた。跳ねました。
Oh, NePoLaBo is... / Did it jump? / It jumped. It jumped up.

667
