あ、買っててよかった！Ah, wait. I ended up buying.
Ah, I'm glad I bought some! / Ah, wait. I ended up buying.

668
01:04:36,596 --> 01:04:44,096
売却して2万。やばい。売るか。ま、いっか。
Sold them for 20,000. / Crazy. / Should I sell? Well, whatever.

669
01:04:44,096 --> 01:04:52,096
ま、いっか。バイ、バイ。
Well, whatever. Buy high...

670
