今回は、出れなくなるかも。
This time, I might not be able to get out.

684
01:07:28,104 --> 01:07:35,104
ね？そうですね、楽しいのが一番大事っていうか。
Right? That's right, having fun is the most important thing, I guess.

685
01:07:35,104 --> 01:07:44,104
どの仕事しても、楽しい仕事やりたい。
No matter what job, I want to do a fun job.

686
