じゃあ、ここで...
Well, from here...

714
01:10:59,312 --> 01:11:01,412
ここで下に行く？
Should I go down from here?

715
01:11:03,312 --> 01:11:06,312
ここちょっと、壁を作って...
Let me make a wall here...

716
01:11:06,312 --> 01:11:08,612
ここは行けない。
Can't go this way.

717
01:11:16,912 --> 01:11:18,612
で、ここで...
So, here...

718
01:11:19,512 --> 01:11:21,412
マーキングをして。
let's make a marking.

719
01:11:21,912 --> 01:11:23,112
そう。
Yes.

720
01:11:23,712 --> 01:11:25,412
で、ここから行く。
And let's go from here.

721
01:11:29,912 --> 01:11:32,012
マイナス、何だっけ？
Minus... what was it again?

722
01:11:32,012 --> 01:11:33,612
もう覚えてない。
I don't remember anymore.

723
01:11:39,812 --> 01:11:41,612
50...57だっけ？
50... was it 57?

724
01:11:42,612 --> 01:11:44,312
56？
56?

725
01:11:45,412 --> 01:11:46,612
いや。
No.

726
01:11:47,412 --> 01:11:48,912
いける。
I can do this.

727
01:11:52,612 --> 01:11:54,612
いや、なんか...
Wait, is it...

728
01:11:55,412 --> 01:11:57,112
明るくなってる？
getting brighter?

729
01:11:57,112 --> 01:11:58,312
気のせい？
Just my imagination?

730
01:12:03,312 --> 01:12:04,612
38。
38.

731
01:12:20,112 --> 01:12:23,112
Do I speak English too? A little bit.

732
01:12:24,112 --> 01:12:25,412
おっ。
Oh.

733
01:12:33,612 --> 01:12:36,612
Oh, it's bright, maybe I should leave it.

734
01:12:43,612 --> 01:12:45,612
That was the sound for a cave, right?

735
01:12:53,112 --> 01:12:55,612
おっ、もうすぐじゃん。
Oh, almost there.

736
01:13:07,612 --> 01:13:09,612
52...

737
01:13:15,912 --> 01:13:17,112
55...

738
01:13:18,912 --> 01:13:20,312
56...

739
01:13:23,912 --> 01:13:25,612
ここから右。
From here, to the right.

740
01:13:42,312 --> 01:13:45,112
Pika pika stone~

741
01:13:45,112 --> 01:13:47,312
Pika pika stone~

742
01:13:51,612 --> 01:13:54,112
Pika pika stone~

743
01:14:06,112 --> 01:14:09,612
Pika pika stone~

744
01:14:22,112 --> 01:14:24,112
来ないかな？
Is it not coming?

745
01:14:36,312 --> 01:14:38,312
来ないかな？
Is it not coming?

746
01:14:39,312 --> 01:14:41,112
Can Towa just buy it?

747
01:14:41,112 --> 01:14:43,312
But it's different!

748
01:14:50,112 --> 01:14:52,612
あつまるのは、なんか two over, right?
Collecting them is like... two over, right?

749
01:15:09,620 --> 01:15:11,120
違うんだよ
No, that's not it.

750
01:15:11,320 --> 01:15:15,120
自分の手で作るの
Creating it with your own hands...

751
01:15:15,620 --> 01:15:19,620
その気持ちの意味は分かるかい
Do you understand the meaning of that feeling?

752
01:16:03,120 --> 01:16:07,620
欲しい、ピカピカストーン
I want... shiny stone.

753
01:16:12,120 --> 01:16:16,620
いや、本当に出る？出ない？
No, will it really show up? Or not?

754
01:16:34,120 --> 01:16:36,120
あ、ゴールド
Oh, gold.

755
01:17:01,120 --> 01:17:04,620
みんな、Only Yen。そう、I think so.
Everyone's like, "Only Yen." Yeah, I think so.

756
