Redstone torches... do they work?

757
01:17:19,520 --> 01:17:21,120
How do you make it again?

758
01:17:21,320 --> 01:17:23,820
Are they bright enough?

759
01:17:25,620 --> 01:17:28,120
They are! You're a genius!

760
01:17:30,620 --> 01:17:32,620
暗くない！
It's not dark!

761
01:17:34,620 --> 01:17:36,620
暗い...
It's dark...

762
01:17:43,120 --> 01:17:46,120
いや、いっぱい作ろうか。
